# Orquestrador RPG

**Infra:** [`docs/infrastructure.md`](../../docs/infrastructure.md) · **Arquitetura:** [`docs/architecture.md`](../../docs/architecture.md)

Monorepo **API only**: `database/` + `src/` Nest. Frontend Next.js = repo separado.

## Roteamento

| Contexto | Rules | Skills |
|----------|-------|--------|
| Infra | — | `docs/infrastructure.md` |
| Arquitetura / BC / CQRS | bounded-contexts, catalog-thin-layer, game-domain | nestjs-bounded-context, cqrs-catalog-vs-game |
| REST / Swagger / erros / testes | rest-api, api-errors, api-testing | nestjs-swagger, nestjs-api-tests |
| Plano API (checklist) | — | [`docs/api-plan.md`](../../docs/api-plan.md) |
| SQL / migrations / seeds | postgres-sql, supabase-sql, sql-clean-code, sql-oop-patterns, phb-data-model | postgres-apply-catalog, rpg-catalog-model |
| Nest catálogo (`src/catalog/`) | catalog-thin-layer, nestjs-core, nestjs-typeorm, api-contract | nest-phb-api, typeorm-rpg-entities |
| Nest game (`src/game/`) | game-domain, bounded-contexts, supabase-auth | cqrs-catalog-vs-game |
| Deploy Vercel | nestjs-vercel | nest-vercel-deploy |
| Supabase DB / Auth | supabase-sql, supabase-auth | supabase-connection, supabase-auth |
| Contrato frontend Next | api-contract | api-consumer-next |
| Relações PHB | phb-data-model | rpg-catalog-model |

## Princípios

- **3 BC:** Catalog (thin), Identity, Game (DDD tático futuro)
- DB + Auth: Supabase · API: Vercel · ORM: TypeORM
- Catálogo read-only público; fichas = JWT + RLS + commands
- `database/` source of truth PHB; `synchronize: false`
